verbose_text: These experiments are consistent with a study performed in cancer cell lines, which shows that the substrate recognition component of SCF, F-box and WD repeat domain containing 7 (Fbw7), elicits its tumor suppressive function by targeting Med13 and Med13L for degradation [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: F-box and WD repeat domain-containing 7 (Fbw7), elicits its tumor suppressive function by targeting Med13 and Med13L
